---
title: Silky Oven-Roasted Eggplant with an Herb and Meyer Lemon Dressing over Tri-Color Quinoa
description: This dish is bursting with fresh, vibrant Mediterranean flavors, although we of course had to incorporate a twist. In addition to traditional ingredients like soft caramelized eggplant, feta cheese, and a lemony herb dressing, we’re throwing in quinoa, the protein-packed Andean grain. You could say it’s a bit of Old World meets New World in a wholesome plate of veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w12-r9-4c89c965.jpg
